By default, which method does HP Network Automation use first to attempt to snapshot
devices?
A. Rlogin with TFTP
B. SSH with CLI - screenscrape
C. SSH with TFTP
D. Telnet with CLI - screenscrape
Answer: C

two.)
A. SNMP
B. SMTP
C. SNTP
D. SFTP
E. NNMi
Answer: A,D
Which method is used for Bastion Host access to devices?
A. RMI
B. CLI
C. TFTP
D. SNMP
Answer: B
